{"id": 1806, "genre": 1000, "title": "竞技综艺节目里哪些环节设置/硬伤你有点烦？", "description": "现在看综艺，有时候就是奔着槽点去的。（题图来自Pixabay)", "record_count": 20315, "comment_count": 58, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170718155541NJk1Vq62hiYP0mId.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-23T17:00:06Z", "questions": [{"id": 2627, "title": "竞技综艺节目里哪些环节设置/硬伤你有点烦？", "content": "竞技综艺节目里哪些环节设置/硬伤你有点烦？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 222622, "content": "嘉宾/导师专业性差，有时候硬着头皮在点评", "image": "img/option/option/20170718155932kvH7Zp8GTPBQtSzg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222625, "content": "嘉宾/导师太抓马，今天发现旷世奇才狂喜，明天又为天才陨落痛心", "image": "img/option/option/201707181600500c9WNoUC7gDkLAHF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222626, "content": "观众配合假嗨，表演投入得像在试镜", "image": "img/option/option/201707181602297348Bvoh1IaMSrdL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222627, "content": "剪辑指向太明确，单独采访互说坏话这种，谁都看出是为了制造冲突", "image": "img/option/option/20170718162153P16byxTImi0FfSn4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222629, "content": "选手言行浮夸，性格刻画靠互撕、比拽、撂狠话", "image": "img/option/option/2017071816054998q1fO4P2SkZBh6D.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222630, "content": "淘汰环节旋律总是温情+励志，“心有多大舞台就有多大”", "image": "img/option/option/20170718160726kCrfxVaAZcKiUGop.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222631, "content": "对比赛的理解流于形式，唱歌比谁会飙高音，嘻哈比谁穿得垮", "image": "img/option/option/201707181608053u5jyzhrqRBo4Nil.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222632, "content": "本地化的手法不高级，说中文都能算“中国元素”", "image": "img/option/option/20170718162030W43BQTfrwZDKcu8S.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222633, "content": "环节比较重复，反正看着都挺像大合唱的", "image": "img/option/option/201707181609306K4fQb0AcgZldRNs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}